data.description: Vestavia School System and the new Pizitz Middle School is conveniently located across the street. 4 bedroom and 3.5 bath home with a true basement. Beautiful bamboo hardwood floors, main level master bedroom, elegant bathroom, formal dining room and eat-in kitchen and family room with gas fireplace. Upstairs has 2 bedrooms, and Jack and Jill bathroom, walk in closet and attic storage. Basement has a full bedroom with bathroom and private entrance which in laws would appreciate. Also a half kitchen w/wet bar and den. 2 car garage with added storage/work space.
